trans-unit.source: Specifies the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.LicenseProvider"></xref> to use with a class.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.LicenseProvider"> </xref> ska användas med en klass.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: When you create a component that you want to license, you must specify the <xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseProvider> by marking the component with a LicenseProviderAttribute.
trans-unit.target: När du skapar en komponent som du vill licens, måste du ange den <xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseProvider>genom att markera komponent med en LicenseProviderAttribute.</xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseProvider>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseProviderAttribute.LicenseProvider%2A> property to get the <xref:System.Type> of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Använd <xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseProviderAttribute.LicenseProvider%2A>egenskapen för att hämta <xref:System.Type>i <xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseProvider>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseProvider> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.ComponentModel.LicenseProviderAttribute.LicenseProvider%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about licensing, see [How to: License Components and Controls](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute> attribute applied to this class has the following <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute.Resources%2A> property value: <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionResource>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute>attribut som används i den här klassen har följande <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute.Resources%2A>egenskapsvärdet: <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionResource>.</xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionResource> </xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute.Resources%2A> </xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute> does not affect desktop applications (which are typically started by double-clicking an icon, typing a command, or entering a URL in a browser).
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute>påverkar inte program (som startas normalt genom att dubbelklicka på en ikon, skriva in ett kommando eller att ange en URL i en webbläsare).</xref:System.Security.Permissions.HostProtectionAttribute>
